OL,4,G0510FAuction
OL,5,     GEhrenbreitstein, one of the
OL,6,     Gfinest paintings by JMW Turner
OL,7,     Gstill in private hands, is up for
OL,8,     Gauction at Sotheby's in London
OL,9,     Gwhere it is expected to fetch
OL,10,     Garound #20million.
OL,11,G0535FAuction
OL,12,     GSotheby's auctions a range of
OL,13,     Gpaintings from the 20th and 21st
OL,14,     Gcenturies which are no bigger
OL,15,     Gthan the size of the catalogue
OL,16,     Gpage on which it is illustrated,
OL,17,     Gin actual size.
